---
/**
 * index.astro — GSFGrace 홈페이지
 * JA First: 일본어가 기본 언어
 */
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="GSFGrace — Hodos Tokyo"
  description="ὁδός. 道. 길. 요14:6 — Receive Life. Become Mercy."
  lang="ja"
>
  <section class="hero">
    <p class="hero-tag">ὁδός — 道 — 길</p>
    <h1 class="hero-title">
      Receive Life.<br />Become Mercy.
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-verse">「わたしは道であり、真理であり、命である」— ヨハネ14:6</p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a href="/story" class="btn-primary" id="hero-story-cta">はじめての方へ →</a>
      <a href="/qa" class="btn-secondary" id="hero-qa-link">疑問に答える</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-intro">
    <p class="section-lead">
      東京・日本橋から、福音をお届けします。<br />
      キリスト教への疑問、信仰と日常、東京での宣教の歩み。
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="section-links" aria-label="コンテンツへのリンク">
    <div class="link-cards">
      <a href="/qa" class="link-card" id="home-qa-card">
        <span class="link-card-icon">❓</span>
        <span class="link-card-label">疑問に答える</span>
        <span class="link-card-desc">なぜ神は苦しみを許すのか？ 科学と信仰は矛盾するか？</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/devotion" class="link-card" id="home-devotion-card">
        <span class="link-card-icon">📖</span>
        <span class="link-card-label">今日のみことば</span>
        <span class="link-card-desc">毎日の短い聖書の黙想</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/walk" class="link-card" id="home-walk-card">
        <span class="link-card-icon">🚶</span>
        <span class="link-card-label">歩みながら</span>
        <span class="link-card-desc">東京での宣教の日々の記録</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/faith-life" class="link-card" id="home-faith-card">
        <span class="link-card-icon">✨</span>
        <span class="link-card-label">信仰と生活</span>
        <span class="link-card-desc">日常の中に見つける福音のかたち</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .hero {
    padding: 4rem 0 3rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero-tag {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: #7c3aed;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: #1c1917;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .hero-verse {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #78716c;
    font-style: italic;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.75rem;
    background: #7c3aed;
    color: #fff;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.15s, transform 0.1s;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: #6d28d9;
    transform: translateY(-1px);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.75rem;
    background: transparent;
    color: #57534e;
    border: 1.5px solid #d6d3d1;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: border-color 0.15s, color 0.15s;
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    border-color: #7c3aed;
    color: #7c3aed;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .section-intro {
    padding: 2rem 0 3rem;
    border-top: 1px solid #e7e5e4;
  }

  .section-lead {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #57534e;
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 1.9;
  }

  .section-links {
    padding: 1rem 0 2rem;
  }

  .link-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .link-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    border: 1px solid #e7e5e4;
    border-radius: 10px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: border-color 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s, transform 0.1s;
    background: #fff;
  }

  .link-card:hover {
    border-color: #c4b5fd;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.08);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .link-card-icon {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  .link-card-label {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1c1917;
  }

  .link-card-desc {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: #78716c;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  @media (max-width: 500px) {
    .link-cards {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
